---
import Divider from "../sub-components/Divider.astro";
---

<section
  class="this-is-how-we relative scroll-mt-20 p-12 pb-0"
  page-section="learn-more"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <h4 class="text-center text-5xl font-bold">This is how we operate</h4>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center py-6 sm:py-12">
      <div class="w-full px-2 py-3 sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-5xl sm:px-0">
        <div class="relative text-base font-medium text-gray-700 antialiased">
          <!-- Vertical bar running through middle -->
          <div
            class="absolute left-1/2 hidden h-full w-1 -translate-x-1/2 transform rounded-full bg-sky-300 sm:block"
          >
          </div>

          <!-- Left section, set by justify-start and sm:pr-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mb-12 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-start transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pr-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Contact:</strong> The customer contacts us with a request
                    to buy a used padel court.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                1
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right section, set by justify-end and sm:pl-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mb-12 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-end transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Consultation:</strong> We consult with the customer to
                    understand their needs and preferences for the padel court they
                    want to buy.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                2
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Left section, set by justify-start and sm:pr-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mb-12 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-start transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pr-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Search:</strong> We use our extensive network and resources
                    to search for a suitable used padel court that matches the customer's
                    requirements.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                3
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right section, set by justify-end and sm:pl-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-end transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Inspection:</strong> Once we have found a suitable used
                    padel court, we inspect it thoroughly to ensure that it meets
                    our high-quality standards.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                4
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Left section, set by justify-start and sm:pr-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mb-12 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-start transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pr-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Delivery:</strong> We coordinate the delivery of the
                    padel court to the customer's location.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                5
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Right section, set by justify-end and sm:pl-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-end transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Installation:</strong> If requested, we can also arrange
                    for the installation of the padel court at the customer's site.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                6
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Left section, set by justify-start and sm:pr-8 -->
          <div class="mt-6 sm:mb-12 sm:mt-0">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center sm:flex-row">
              <div
                class="mx-auto flex w-full items-center justify-start transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1"
              >
                <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pr-8">
                  <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 shadow-md">
                    <strong>Follow-up:</strong> After the delivery and/or installation,
                    we follow up with the customer to ensure that everything has
                    been done to their satisfaction.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="absolute left-1/2 flex h-8 w-8 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-4 transform items-center justify-center rounded-full border-4 border-sky-300 bg-white font-bold sm:translate-y-0"
              >
                7
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="relative z-10 text-lg font-light">
          After we have found a suitable court and inspected it to ensure it
          meets our customer's expectations, we will request a reservation fee
          from the customer. This fee secures the purchase and covers any
          expenses related to dismantling, transportation, and reinstallation of
          the court. The remaining payment is due upon delivery of the court to
          the customer. Our goal is to provide a hassle-free and seamless
          process for our customers, from start to finish.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Divider />
</section>
